  "text": "Next, we consider the mean-square convergence of the projection method with a particular supporting one-step method X. Suppose that the supporting one-step method X is of mean-square order p, then we will prove that the projection methodX with it has the same mean-square order under certain conditions. Here we will make use of the following theorems proposed in [CITATION_1] .",
